If you want to play him mid where i always play him i tend to go something along the lines of 
{{item:3004}} {{item:3142}} {{item:3156}} {{item:3158}} {{item:3036}}  And either {{item:3053}} or {{item:3812}} or {{item:3072}}  depending on what the situation is.  But if you need more defensive item then get {{item:3026}}

Also when playing mid like make sure you ward just outside the turrent range not so close he can notice the ward and you can hide off the lane a little bit in one of the sides and land your q easier that way.
